<title>THERE IS A FOUNTAIN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Imanuel thizam apat,
 Thisan lui a luong ie;
 * Gilo zie luia kisil chuh,
 A gitloh thieng tana. D.S.

[V2]
 2. Gucha thikuon a damlai khan,
 Lui chu mu'n a kipak;
 * Amah bangin gilo mahleng,
 Ka gitloh silthieng ding. D.S.

[V3]
 3. Na liemma apat a lui luong,
 Ginna'n ka muh apat;
 * Lungsiet tatna chuh ka thupi,
 Ka thih masieh hina. D.S.

[V4]
 4. Tieng chuleh la lopi hawihzaw'n,
 Sa'ng ka, Na hatna chuh;
 * Ka lei kamthiemlo, dangawk hi,
 Thana a um tiengleh, D.S.

[V5]
 5. Thisan lui luong chuh ka muh in,
 A hehpih na'n adim;
 * Kumsawt inle kang-ta puona,
 Namtin thienna lui chuh. D.S.</lyrics>
</song>